[01:10.567]When the night is gone, journey will carry on
[01:14.813]To the secret untold, to the wonder we hold
[01:17.916]Running out the woods we know, little sheep we tip tap toe
[01:21.356]I wandered high and low, now I don't walk alone
[01:25.132]Together on we go
[01:28.676]Wuu
[01:32.509]Let's find a way out
[01:36.053]Moon's up high, shining wide.
[01:37.644]Set my heart upon a quest
[01:40.070]I'm by myself, but far from lonely
[01:43.348]Little lamb, wool so white.
[01:44.997]Why're you running on your own?
[01:47.581]I'm just like you, searching for where I belong.
[01:51.405]Ayayayaya Ayayayayayaya
[01:54.925]Wuu
[01:58.522]Round and around, around we go~
